  "prompt": "Is there any dual SIM mobile supporting 4G or 4G and 3G?",
  "response": "Yes, there are many dual SIM mobile phones that support 4G networks, as well as those that can combine 4G and 3G capabilities. Most modern smartphones offer dual SIM functionality with support for 4G LTE on at least one of the SIM slots, and many support 4G on both slots.\n\nHere are some popular brands and models that support dual SIM with 4G:\n\n1. **Samsung Galaxy Series**: Many models in the Galaxy A and Galaxy M series support dual SIM 4G.\n2. **Xiaomi Redmi Series**: Redmi Note and Redmi series devices often come with dual SIM 4G capabilities.\n3. **Realme Smartphones**: Many Realme models support dual SIM with 4G.\n4. **OnePlus Devices**: Most OnePlus smartphones come with dual SIM functionality supporting 4G.\n5. **Vivo and Oppo Phones**: These brands usually offer several models with dual SIM 4G support.\n6. **Nokia Smartphones**: Recent Nokia models also offer dual SIM capabilities with 4G.\n\nMake sure to check the specifications of a specific model to confirm its network capabilities, as they can vary.",
